# MCMC_C

This project executes the Metropolis-Hastling algorithm

## Instalation and Configuration

### Instalation

There is not installation required. Just download the code.

### Configuration

The foler of the project includes a Makefile for the compilation of the source code. Just introduce in terminal the next: ```make main```

It will appear a executable file in the root folder with name ```main```

## Usage

This code is intended to be executed with OpenMP. To assign the number of threads you want to use, you must introduce in terminal the next: ```export OMP_NUM_THREADS=<num_threads>```

To start executing use the next command: ```./main```

